headline: Is Devon Energy Stock Underperforming the Nasdaq?
summary: Devon Energy has struggled to keep up with the broader Nasdaq Composite over the past year, but analysts hold a fairly bullish view of its outlook.

headline: Devon Energy: Integrating Grayson Mill Acquisition But Still Affected By Low Natural Gas Prices
